field.value:
The following throws an exception:

[Transaction]
public virtual bool UpdateTemporaryAttachment()
{
	ITransactionManager manager = IoC.Resolve<ITransactionManager>();
	if(manager.CurrentTransaction!=null)
	{
		manager.CurrentTransaction.Rollback();
	}
}

The issue is that calling rollback will not set rollBackOnly, and when the method exits, it tried to commit.
